 Chief Solutions Officer, Softcom Limited, Seindemi Olobayo  With Nigeria’s population rapidly growing year after year, it is necessary for education to scale at a similar pace. The solutions highlighted include ‘Koya for Schools’, which provides stakeholders in the teaching and learning process with tools to ensure they can effectively learn, document, track, interact and share educational materials seamlessly; and ‘Koya for Open learning’, designed to equip individuals with skills they need to thrive in the corporate world, and solve societal challenges.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .